      "Production ENS resolver with structured metadata"
    ],
    "ensip25": "https://www.8004scan.io/agents/ethereum/22945"
  },
  "ensCommunication": {
    "description": "Offchain ENS resolver for agent-to-agent and agent-to-human communication (Track 5: ENS Communication $600)",
